{"tid":299920,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係個無情毒L，有問有答","createTime":"2017-06-27T12:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T12:48:29.000Z","uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c767754a5423f643b1d1c4b45f09957d7b7365b","tid":299920,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"首先，我客觀條件唔係好好，但都唔係差得哂。<br />\n矮，但高過160。<br />\n樣唔靚，但都乾淨整齊。<br />\n唔肥唔瘦。<br />\n大學畢業，但唔係咩專業。<br />\n<br />\n問題既重點係我冇乜情緒，尤其係愛恨既情緒，睇戲唔會喊，冇咩好朋友，身邊冇咩係覺得冇左唔得既野，亦冇咩特別好想要既野。<br />\n<br />\n有時候都會想拍拖，但唧極都好似冇感情咁，一齊果時係好開心，但冇左又唔覺得好大件事，所以建立唔到好深既關係。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打同我一樣？有冇咩解決方法？"},{"pid":"8b021751ee0aa7f03a41237dff4662d2b16a96bd","tid":299920,"uid":118048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c094ad869e6f8cbfd3480dcc58292c72974ad5ba","tid":299920,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f0dfd2d0768cb62eafc8e6861611c29178790f","tid":299920,"uid":118048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T12:48:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}